<A>__{bill ushering them deeper into the house... quick intros to a few guests as they pass... sam, lynn, and paige taking it all in... starting to sense the dimensions of this massive house... the waiters in their pressed jackets offering them food... the extravagance... like nothing they've ever seen... ... bill pulling sam off from the crowd so it's just the two of them... taking an envelope from his jacket and handing it to him...}
